IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. CharacterCount.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
   01 WS-STRING PIC X(50).
   01 WS-COUNT PIC 9(2) VALUE 0.
   01 WS-I PIC 9(2).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "Enter a string: " WITH NO ADVANCING.
    ACCEPT WS-STRING.

    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-STRING
       IF WS-STRING(WS-I:1) NOT = SPACE
          ADD 1 TO WS-COUNT
       END-IF
    END-PERFORM.

    DISPLAY "Number of characters: " WS-COUNT.
    STOP RUN.
